Use heap to have constant time for finding the lexical smaller next airport and do dfs on that.
```
class Solution:
    def findItinerary(self, tickets: List[List[str]]) -> List[str]:
        graph = defaultdict(list)
        for start, end in tickets:
            heappush(graph[start], end)
        itinerary = []
        def dfs(airport):
            while graph[airport]:
                next_airport = heappop(graph[airport])
                dfs(next_airport)
            itinerary.append(airport)

        dfs("JFK")
        return itinerary[::-1]
```
